  <!-- EN: Bionic stomach-Earth -->
  <RI_Hediff_EarthBionicStomach.label>戍土鼎胃</RI_Hediff_EarthBionicStomach.label>
  <!-- EN: An installed prosthetic heart. It contains an electric motor that pumps blood smoothly around the body. Users often report feeling tired, but it's better than the alternative. -->
  <RI_Hediff_EarthBionicStomach.description>脾胃为气血生化之源、后天之本，藏意，在五行属土。\n\n这颗以神工巧机打造的精妙仿生胃，可以在胃部开辟第二金丹，辅助吸收灵气。</RI_Hediff_EarthBionicStomach.description>
  <!-- EN: Bionic stomach-Earth -->
  <RI_Hediff_EarthBionicStomach.labelNoun>戍土鼎胃</RI_Hediff_EarthBionicStomach.labelNoun>
  
  <!-- EN: Bionic heart-Fire -->
  <RI_Hediff_FireBionicHeart.label>千壶焱心</RI_Hediff_FireBionicHeart.label>
  <!-- EN: An installed prosthetic heart. It contains an electric motor that pumps blood smoothly around the body. Users often report feeling tired, but it's better than the alternative. -->
  <RI_Hediff_FireBionicHeart.description>心为神之居、血之主、脉之宗，在五行属火。\n\n这颗以神工巧机打造的精妙仿生心脏，可以代替原有心脏，迸发强大活力，令全身血液循环与灵气交融，提升修炼速度。</RI_Hediff_FireBionicHeart.description>
  <!-- EN: Bionic heart-Fire -->
  <RI_Hediff_FireBionicHeart.labelNoun>千壶焱心</RI_Hediff_FireBionicHeart.labelNoun>
  
