  <!-- EN: Bionic lung-Metal -->
  <RI_Hediff_MetalBionicLung.label>肃金御肺</RI_Hediff_MetalBionicLung.label>
  <!-- EN: This exquisitely crafted artificial lung, created with divine skill and precision, can accommodate the spirit of heaven and earth, one breath and one breath, heaven and earth are connected. -->
  <RI_Hediff_MetalBionicLung.description>肺为魄之处、气之主。在五行属金。\n\n这颗以神工巧机打造的精妙仿生肺，可以容纳天地灵气，一呼一吸间，天地相通。</RI_Hediff_MetalBionicLung.description>
  <!-- EN: Bionic lung-Metal -->
  <RI_Hediff_MetalBionicLung.labelNoun>肃金御肺</RI_Hediff_MetalBionicLung.labelNoun>
  
  <!-- EN: Bionic kidney-Water -->
  <RI_Hediff_WaterBionicKidney.label>寒灵水肾</RI_Hediff_WaterBionicKidney.label>
  <!-- EN: This ingenious bionic kidney can replace the original kidney and enhance the filtration system. -->
  <RI_Hediff_WaterBionicKidney.description>肾为先天之本，藏志，腰为肾之腑，在五行属水。\n\n这颗以神工巧机打造的精妙仿生肾脏，可以代替原有肾脏，加强过滤系统。</RI_Hediff_WaterBionicKidney.description>
  <!-- EN: Bionic kidney-Water -->
  <RI_Hediff_WaterBionicKidney.labelNoun>寒灵水肾</RI_Hediff_WaterBionicKidney.labelNoun>
  
  <!-- EN: Bionic liver-Wood -->
  <RI_Hediff_WoodBionicLiver.label>棠木枝肝</RI_Hediff_WoodBionicLiver.label>
  <!-- EN: This exquisite bionic liver built by a clever machine can expel toxins from the body faster, wash the marrow and forge the body, and enhance immunity. -->
  <RI_Hediff_WoodBionicLiver.description>肝为魂之处，血之藏，筋之宗。在五行属木，主升主动。\n\n这颗以神工巧机打造的精妙仿生肝，可以将毒素更快地排出体外，洗髓锻体，增强免疫力。</RI_Hediff_WoodBionicLiver.description>
  <!-- EN: Bionic liver-Wood -->
  <RI_Hediff_WoodBionicLiver.labelNoun>棠木枝肝</RI_Hediff_WoodBionicLiver.labelNoun>
  
